data.description: Say hello to 3235 Schilling Street. This home offers 4 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms and a  finished basement. This home has so many recent updates all within the last two years; brand new furnace, AC, and ductwork, new water heater, freshly painted kitchen cabinets with new hardware, resurfaced countertops, new backsplash and trim, new vinyl plank flooring in the living room and kitchen, and new light fixtures throughout.
